  "description": "xtrakt UI primitives for Angular — XBreadcrumb, XShell, XButton (component + xButton directive), XInput, XField, XCard, XBadge, XLoading, XEmpty, XAlert. Standalone, ships source TypeScript; consumers compile as part of their app.",
  "license": "UNLICENSED",
